<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CBS Case Study Challenge 2025</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        :root {
            --dark-bg: #0a0a0a;
            --dark-surface: #121212;
            --dark-card: #1a1a1a;
            --dark-text: #e0e0e0;
            --primary: #2563eb;
            --secondary: #3b82f6;
            --accent: #60a5fa;
            --light: #1f1f1f;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--dark-bg);
            color: var(--dark-text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-surface), var(--dark-card));
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .event-logo {
            width: 130px;
            height: 130px;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border: 4px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            margin: 0 auto 25px;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease, box-shadow 0.5s ease;
        }

        .event-logo:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.5);
        }

        .event-logo i {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: white;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, var(--accent));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 35px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .stat-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            min-width: 220px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .stat-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587825140708-dfaf72ae4b04?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
            padding: 120px 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: var(--secondary);
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.8;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .about {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: var(--dark-surface);
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 120px;
            height: 5px;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        .about-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 50px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .about-text {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .about-text p {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .about-image {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .about-image:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            filter: grayscale(20%) brightness(85%);
            transition: transform 0.5s ease, filter 0.5s ease;
        }

        .about-image:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            filter: grayscale(0%) brightness(100%);
        }

        .event-gallery {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 60px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            position: relative;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
        }

        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 280px;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
            filter: grayscale(20%) brightness(85%);
            transition: transform 0.5s ease, filter 0.5s ease;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.08);
            filter: grayscale(0%) brightness(100%);
        }

        .rounds {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: var(--dark-bg);
        }

        .round-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .round {
            background: var(--dark-card);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 40px;
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            border-top: 5px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .round:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px);
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
        }

        .round h3 {
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.7rem;
        }

        .round p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .round-icon {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
        }

        .challenge {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: var(--dark-surface);
        }

        .challenge-content {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .challenge-box {
            background: var(--dark-card);
            border-left: 6px solid var(--accent);
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            text-align: left;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .challenge-box ul {
            margin-left: 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .challenge-box li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .challenge-box li::before {
            content: "â€¢";
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 1em;
            margin-left: -1em;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .judges {
            padding: 100px 0;
            background: var(--dark-bg);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .judges p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #1e40af);
            color: white;
            padding: 100px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .highlight-content {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .highlight h2 {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .highlight p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .partners {
            padding: 100px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background: var(--dark-surface);
        }

        .partner-logos {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 50px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .partner-logo {
            background: var(--dark-card);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            width: 180px;
            height: 180px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .partner-logo:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
        }

        .partner-logo i {
            font-size: 65px;
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .partner-logo span {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .stats {
                gap: 20px;
            }

            .stat-item {
                min-width: 160px;
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .stat-number {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 80px 0;
            }

            .hero h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .event-gallery {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .section-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
        <header>
            <div class="container header-content">
                <div class="event-logo">
                    <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
                </div>
                <h1>CBS Case Study Challenge</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">Under Crescendo's CBS Business Championship 2025</p>
                <p class="subtitle">Powered by CBS | In Collaboration with Ecovision and Grandeur</p>

                <div class="stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">600+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Registrations</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">35K+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Attendees</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">10</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Finalist Teams</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container hero-content">
                <h2>Synergy's Flagship Academic Event</h2>
                <p>The CBS Case Study Challenge brought together participants from across India to solve real-world
                    business
                    problems under Crescendo, the annual cultural and management fest.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">About the Event</h2>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <div class="about-text">
                        <p>As Synergy's flagship academic initiative, the CBS Case Study Challenge was organised under
                            Crescendo, the annual cultural and management fest that draws over 35,000 attendees.</p>
                        <p>In collaboration with Ecovision and Grandeur, the event brought together participants from
                            across
                            India to solve real-world business problems.</p>
                        <p>The challenge saw 600+ registrations. Ten finalist teams after surviving 2 preliminary
                            rounds,
                            tackled strategies for Luminous on diamonds, positioning, perceptions, and channel mix.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-image">
                        <img src="/images/CBS/CBS.png" alt="Students collaborating">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="event-gallery">
                    <div class="gallery-item">
                        <img src="/images/CBS/CBS 1.png" alt="Event presentation">
                    </div>
                    <div class="gallery-item">
                        <img src="/images/CBS/CBS 2.png" alt="Winners celebration">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="rounds">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Competition Structure</h2>
                <div class="round-container">
                    <div class="round">
                        <div class="round-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Round 1: Case Submission</h3>
                        <p>Teams submitted their detailed case analyses and proposed solutions to the business challenge
                            presented by Luminous.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="round">
                        <div class="round-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-chalkboard"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Round 2: Final Presentation</h3>
                        <p>Shortlisted teams presented their strategies to a panel of judges, demonstrating innovative
                            thinking and practical solutions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="challenge">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">The Challenge</h2>
                <div class="challenge-content">
                    <div class="challenge-box">
                        <p>Participants developed strategies for Luminous to:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Explore entry into the diamond business</li>
                            <li>Analyze positioning and market perception</li>
                            <li>Design an effective channel mix strategy</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="judges">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Panel of Judges</h2>
                <p>The final presentations were evaluated by industry experts and faculty members, ensuring a fair and
                    insightful assessment of each team's strategies.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="highlight">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="highlight-content">
                    <h2>Celebrating Innovation</h2>
                    <p>The CBS Case Study Challenge continues to be a platform that nurtures future leaders by providing
                        real-world business exposure and celebrating innovation and problem-solving excellence.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="partners">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">In Collaboration With</h2>
                <div class="partner-logos">
                    <div class="partner-logo">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                        <span>Ecovision</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="partner-logo">
                        <i class="fas fa-crown"></i>
                        <span>Grandeur</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>


</body>

